    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline rend="right">
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1887-04-10">April 10 [1887] noon</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear friend</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I return you the cards signed&#8212;(Isn't there a mistake in the date? Ought it not
                to be marked right? Thursday Evn'g is the <hi rend="italic">14th</hi>&#8212;not the
                15th)&#8212;</p>
            <p>If convenient I think I will go on from here say on the 9 a m train Thursday from the
                depot here&#8212;but come over to-morrow &amp; let's have it fixed for
                certain&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
